title: Dub FX - Theory of Harmony (2013) [FLAC]
description:
New Dub FX Album entitled Theory of Harmony

Downloaded in FLAC straight from the Pledge Campaign.

Dub FX has said he doesn't mind his work being shared, but if you enjoy this album please be sure to buy a copy to support a hardworking indie artist.

Includes all 13 songs, the exclusive pledge campaign bonus track as well as all of the album artwork.

You can buy the full album here: http://store.dubfx.net/
